      "writtenOn": "2019-11-07T20:45:41Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I was under the impression that by using puppeteer, we can make sure we know what version of Chrome we are testing against. Is that not desired?",
      "revId": "e67fab2f2e75fd3a4f72c242d5ccd0be34190529",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02",
